Source: regolith-styles
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ken Gilmer <kgilmer@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11)
Standards-Version: 4.1.3
Homepage: https://regolith-linux.org

Package: regolith-styles
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Theme and style definitions for Regolith Linux
 Provides common Xresource files that can be shared among Regolith Looks.

Package: regolith-look-cahuella
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, arc-icon-theme, cahuella, fonts-materialdesignicons-webfont, fonts-source-code-pro-ttf
Provides: regolith-look
Description: Regolith R1.3 look
 Cahuella is a Nord based look with Materal Design icons.

Package: regolith-look-nord
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, arc-icon-theme, nordic, fonts-font-awesome, fonts-source-code-pro-ttf
Provides: regolith-look
Description: Regolith R1.2 look
 Nord Look takes the default fontawesome solarized theme but changes
 the color scheme to Nord.

Package: regolith-look-ayu
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, ayu-theme, arc-icon-theme, fonts-font-awesome, fonts-source-code-pro-ttf
Provides: regolith-look
Description: Ayu look
 Ayu is a light color theme with bold colors and the fontawesome icons.

Package: regolith-look-ayu-dark
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, ayu-theme, arc-icon-theme, fonts-font-awesome, fonts-source-code-pro-ttf
Provides: regolith-look
Description: Ayu Dark look
 Ayu Dark is a dark color theme with bold colors and fontawesome icons.

Package: regolith-look-ayu-mirage
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, ayu-theme, arc-icon-theme, fonts-font-awesome, fonts-source-code-pro-ttf
Provides: regolith-look
Description: Ayu Mirage look
 Ayu Mirage is a dark but lighter than ayu-dark theme with fontawesome icons.

Package: regolith-look-lascaille
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, ayu-theme, moka-icon-theme, fonts-materialdesignicons-webfont, fonts-jetbrains-mono
Provides: regolith-look
Conflicts: regolith-look-ayu-mirage-regolith
Replaces: regolith-look-ayu-mirage-regolith
Description: Default R1.4 look based on Ayu Mirage and JetBrains Mono
 Based on Ayu Mirage, this look includes Material Design icons and
 visual tweaks to Rofi and i3.

Package: regolith-look-solarized-dark
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, arc-icon-theme, solarc-theme, fonts-font-awesome, fonts-source-code-pro-ttf
Conflicts: regolith-assets
Provides: regolith-look
Description: Solarized Dark look
 A Regolith look featuring the Solarized Dark color palette and
 fontawesome icons. This is the original Regolith theme.

Package: regolith-look-ubuntu
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, adwaita-icon-theme, fonts-font-awesome, fonts-ubuntu, ubuntu-wallpapers
Provides: regolith-look
Description: Ubuntu look for Ubuntu style
 A Ubuntu-themed look that tries to maintain the default Ubuntu feel
 while integrating the Regolith UI.

Package: regolith-look-gruvbox
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, gruvbox-gtk, moka-icon-theme, fonts-materialdesignicons-webfont, fonts-jetbrains-mono
Provides: regolith-look
Description: User contributed gruvbox theme
 Colors based on https://github.com/morhetz/gruvbox

Package: regolith-look-dracula
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, dracula-gtk, moka-icon-theme, fonts-materialdesignicons-webfont, fonts-jetbrains-mono
Provides: regolith-look
Description: User contributed Dracula theme
 Colors based on https://draculatheme.com/gtk

Package: regolith-look-pop-os
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, pop-gtk-theme, pop-icon-theme, fonts-font-awesome, pop-fonts
Provides: regolith-look
Description: User contributed Pop!_OS theme
 Default theme of https://pop.system76.com/.

Package: regolith-look-midnight
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, regolith-styles, fonts-materialdesignicons-webfont
Provides: regolith-look
Description: User contributed theme based on the midnight theme (https://github.com/i-mint/midnight) and qogir icons (https://github.com/vinceliuice/Qogir-icon-theme/).
